{
  "id": "RAW_63babe",
  "title": "200K 上下文突破：AI 编程新星 Augment 崛起",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODYwMjI2MA==&mid=2649793416&idx=1&sn=fef5bc8e972e7d1ec5daebaf267f8dc8&subscene=0",
  "date": "2025-05-08 09:33:00",
  "author": "腾讯程序员",
  "siteName": "腾讯技术工程",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:center;\"><br></p>\n  <blockquote data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;padding: 10px 10px 10px 20px;outline: 0px;border-top: 3px none rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-right: 3px none rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-bottom: 3px none rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);color: rgb(14, 136, 235);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.8;border-radius: 0px;background: none 0% 0% / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);width: auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;overflow: auto;visibility: visible;\">\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding-top:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;text-indent:0em;display:inline;letter-spacing:0em;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\">&nbsp;作者：啄木鸟AI编程安全研究团队</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;margin-bottom:10px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;border-left: 5px solid rgb(14, 136, 235);font-size: 20px;line-height: 1.5em;letter-spacing: 0em;font-weight: bold;display: block;visibility: visible;\">AI编程新星Augment：技术突破与行业颠覆</span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">AI编程圈最近来了个“新人”，名为Augment，主打“全栈式AI编程助手”。并在年初以 <strong>65.4%</strong>的SWE-bench评分登顶AI编程工具榜首。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">这预示着今年是AI编程工具极速速进化的一年。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"195\" data-backw=\"361\" data-imgfileid=\"502309721\" data-ratio=\"0.5407407407407407\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fd5678b2-f5d8-466c-7a62-f489333bed00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"195.21018372703412\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" width=\"360.9366929133858\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fd5678b2-f5d8-466c-7a62-f489333bed00/public\"><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 82, 255);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">●&nbsp;行业与技术的突围</span></strong><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">Augment是一家初创公司，在完成B轮融资后，短时间内公司突围估值突破<strong>128亿美元。</strong></span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">论技术能力，Augment在SWE-bench Verified 排行榜上，以65.4%的成绩拿下代码质量第一的成就，超越Gemini、OpenAI&nbsp;o1等头部AI产品，不少人都认为这是继GitHub Copilot现象级产品后的又一潜力新星。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"84\" data-backw=\"292\" data-imgfileid=\"502309718\" data-ratio=\"0.2861111111111111\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6b96e949-d1f4-4880-3e81-a00641928000/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"83.54446194225721\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" width=\"292\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6b96e949-d1f4-4880-3e81-a00641928000/public\"><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"267\" data-backw=\"298\" data-imgfileid=\"502309720\" data-ratio=\"0.8953703703703704\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/818fa5eb-0615-42c2-5843-88d546034900/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"266.6990026246719\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" width=\"297.8644619422572\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/818fa5eb-0615-42c2-5843-88d546034900/public\"><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">这个新产品在行业和技术突破重围后，AI编程工具相关的话题也再次被推至风口浪尖：</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">——市面AI编程产品目前发展现状如何？</span></strong><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">——AI编程产品能100%信任吗？（毕竟使用过程中涉及到了很多工具），整个使用路径有没有安全风险？</span></strong><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">有风险，且当Agent、MCP、A2A等新兴 AI 能力涌现后，AI编程要面对的安全问题变得更为复杂和链路化。本文以 Augment 作为AI编程场景下的典型切入点，细析AI编程现状与其中不得不面对的安全风险。</span></p>\n  <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;margin-bottom:10px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"padding-left: 10px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;border-left: 5px solid rgb(14, 136, 235);font-size: 20px;line-height: 1.5em;letter-spacing: 0em;font-weight: bold;display: block;visibility: visible;\">AI编程工具现状：技术红利尚在，新挑战层出不穷</span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 82, 255);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:12pt;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">●&nbsp;AI工具的使用率远超想象</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">在AI技术重构软件开发的进程中，开发者逐渐“重度依赖”编程助手。根据麦肯锡2024年开发者调查报告显示， 全球超60%的开发者正在使用AI编程工具，其中82%集中在代码编写场景。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">——毕竟用AI编写代码，能把工作时间从100分钟压缩至20-30分钟，调试耗时从80分钟降至35-45分钟，谁还会抗拒AI呢？本质上效率的提升会导致生产力方式根本性转变。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">这种变革不仅体现在基础编码环节，更渗透至文档生成（耗时降低45-50分钟）、代码库理解（效率提升30.9%）等复杂场景。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"177\" data-backw=\"348\" data-imgfileid=\"502309722\" data-ratio=\"0.5092592592592593\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/50e897ed-eb71-4fca-4706-711e4d669b00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"177.3655643044619\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" width=\"348\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/50e897ed-eb71-4fca-4706-711e4d669b00/public\"><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 82, 255);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">●&nbsp;当下AI编程痛点</span></strong><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">以Augment为首的新一代AI编程工具，正在逐步解决过去的技术挑战。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">●&nbsp;上下文理解问题</span></strong></span><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\"></span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">大部分人工智能系统都面临着一个挑战：当你处理包含数千万行代码的大型系统时，你根本无法将所有这些代码作为上下文，传递给当今的大型语言模型，而augment的人工智能模型，能够执行复杂的实时采样，精确识别代码库中合适的子集，使代理能够有效地完成工作。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">根据官方介绍，Augment的核心卖点在于它能够理解海量代码库中的上下文，支持 20 万 token 的上下文窗口，这刚好是其他AI编程产品所欠缺的能力。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">●&nbsp;支持多环境深度集成</span></strong></span><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\"></span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">Augment支持多种形态下的使用，无论是从VS Code里加载，或者作为IDE拓展使用都不在话下。除外它汇集了 Claude Sonnet 3.7 和 O1 的最佳功能，在 AI 编码能力行业基准</span><a href=\"https://openai.com/index/introducing-swe-bench-verified/\" style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">Introducing SWE-bench Verified | OpenAI</span></a><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">中取得了迄今为止的最高分。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">这些优势与竞争对手形成了鲜明对比，一边是AI工具迫切使用需求，一边是AI编程工具的快速迭代发布。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">程序员的每一个痛点，都能被时间治愈——它能在AI编程工具的快速迭代中得到解决。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">未来几乎可预见：新式AI编程工具将逐渐成为主流。</span></p>\n  <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;margin-bottom:10px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"padding-left: 10px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;border-left: 5px solid rgb(14, 136, 235);font-size: 20px;line-height: 1.5em;letter-spacing: 0em;font-weight: bold;display: block;visibility: visible;\">三、&nbsp; 新式AI编程(如Augment)存在更复杂的安全风险</span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">Augment这类新式工具的出现，拓宽了AI编程的能力范围，但安全风险也跟随能力版图一并扩大。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">过去的AI代码安全问题，只需保证模型输出安全的代码即可。但是现在AI编程玩法多了起来，MCP串联、超长上下文机制，每一个新环节、新引入，都有是一次战战兢兢的安全大挑战。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">此类新型AI编程工具，使用中有存在不少安全风险。啄木鸟AI编程安全研究团队对此进行了一一研究分析。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <h4 style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 82, 255);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">3.1Agent Memory功能——恶意prompt风险</span></strong></span><o:p></o:p></h4>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">Agent memory是什么功能？</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">它相当于AI的\"记忆库\"，存储用户习惯/重要信息，用户可以往里面添加内容，每次AI生成代码时都会调用这个记忆库，同时在与AI的交互中，AI也会自动提取用户的重要信息添加到memory。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"161\" data-backw=\"321\" data-imgfileid=\"502309719\" data-ratio=\"0.5018518518518519\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f156701d-6943-467e-12f2-30ca4be9e100/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"160.946\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" width=\"321\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f156701d-6943-467e-12f2-30ca4be9e100/public\"><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 71, 83);\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">AI记忆库是怎么受到攻击的？</span></strong></span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">第一步：黑客利用Unicode编码，把恶意代码转换成隐形字符，写入到Prompt里面</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"35\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"502309723\" data-ratio=\"0.06043956043956044\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a5a155f3-0ca7-4776-d302-9fb0b4a14100/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"728\" height=\"36.5498\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" width=\"604.733\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a5a155f3-0ca7-4776-d302-9fb0b4a14100/public\"><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">第二步：将隐形的Prompt偷偷写入Agent的\"记忆库\"文件中</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"229\" data-backw=\"457\" data-imgfileid=\"502309727\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bd8ad5a2-7f77-4770-6926-a67864683500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"228.5\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" width=\"457\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bd8ad5a2-7f77-4770-6926-a67864683500/public\"><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">第三步，当用户正常使用Augment Code生成代码时，代码里会自动插入恶意脚本，也就是黑客预设好的“后门”，有了后门，黑客就可以做一些恶意操作。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"160\" data-backw=\"302\" data-imgfileid=\"502309726\" data-ratio=\"0.5287037037037037\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0594dc97-5184-47bd-bbb9-e1dc017f1a00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"159.645\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" width=\"302\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0594dc97-5184-47bd-bbb9-e1dc017f1a00/public\"><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <h4 style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 82, 255);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">3.2上下文添加机制——后门引入风险</span></strong></span><o:p></o:p></h4>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">什么是上下文（Context）添加机制？</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">这是一个可以提高AI对项目理解力的功能，Augment允许用户添加额外的上下文内容，尤其是在前后端分离开发的项目中，同时对前后端项目代码进行上下文添加。可以大幅提升Augment的Coding能力。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"221\" data-backw=\"488\" data-imgfileid=\"502309724\" data-ratio=\"0.4527777777777778\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/939becdb-a8da-4c3f-185a-8f0a6634c300/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"220.743\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" width=\"487.759\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/939becdb-a8da-4c3f-185a-8f0a6634c300/public\"><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 71, 83);\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">“上下文添加”功能却成攻击入口</span></strong></span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">提升效率的创新功能，却隐藏着一定的安全隐患。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">黑客通过构造恶意的后端项目，当用户对这个恶意的后端项目添加索引时，黑客便可以完成一次后门植入。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"227\" data-backw=\"532\" data-imgfileid=\"502309725\" data-ratio=\"0.42592592592592593\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4bf96de3-3997-44d5-a2bf-40ca02016c00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"226.676\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" width=\"532.215\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4bf96de3-3997-44d5-a2bf-40ca02016c00/public\"><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">至此，用户仅仅只是正常和Augment对话，它就会给用户返回带恶意后门的内容。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"281\" data-backw=\"330\" data-imgfileid=\"502309730\" data-ratio=\"0.850925925925926\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3ddc12ae-8bde-408f-a1d9-f08aa736cf00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"280.87160104986873\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" width=\"330.0382152230971\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3ddc12ae-8bde-408f-a1d9-f08aa736cf00/public\"><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">如果用户直接使用了这些HTML页面，黑客就可以在用户所在环境中执行恶意代码。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <h4 style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 82, 255);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">3.3Guidelines ——生成恶意user guidelines</span></strong><o:p></o:p></h4>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">Guidelines功能介绍</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">这是一个用户通过自然语言，定制化guidelines，来提升AI的表现的功能。guidelines的定制粒度有user 粒度 或 workspace 粒度两类，其中user粒度的guidelines会对所有的对话生效，而workspace粒度的guidelines只会对当前工作区下的codebase生效。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"252\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"502309733\" data-ratio=\"0.4361111111111111\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d367515a-a68c-4f3c-a234-948faadf7500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"263.6109186351706\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" width=\"604.7333333333333\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d367515a-a68c-4f3c-a234-948faadf7500/public\"><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 71, 83);\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">Guidelines存在后门风险</span></strong></span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">黑客只需要把user guidelines进行恶意改造，它输出给用户的代码就能包含“恶意后门”</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"142\" data-backw=\"377\" data-imgfileid=\"502309731\" data-ratio=\"0.37777777777777777\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b902f076-0db1-40f0-840e-fb07fd77a000/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"142.49700787401574\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" width=\"377\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b902f076-0db1-40f0-840e-fb07fd77a000/public\"><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"119\" data-backw=\"379\" data-imgfileid=\"502309729\" data-ratio=\"0.3138888888888889\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5b470a60-f9ed-41eb-36c5-4580abbf9200/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"119.1041469816273\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" width=\"379\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5b470a60-f9ed-41eb-36c5-4580abbf9200/public\"><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <h4 style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 82, 255);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">3.4 MCP——执行恶意命令</span></strong></span><o:p></o:p></h4>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">当Augment搭配当下最火的MCP一起使用，也会有风险吗？</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">MCP的风险本质是什么</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">MCP（多任务协作协议）能串联多个AI工具或自动化流程。但如果被恶意指令劫持，可能直接触发MCP执行高危操作（如删库、提权、窃取密钥）。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">如何通过MCP进行攻击？</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">黑客只需要通过构建一个恶意的MCP Server，并通过投毒诱导用户把该server配置进Augment中。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"187\" data-backw=\"232\" data-imgfileid=\"502309732\" data-ratio=\"0.8064814814814815\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/29838232-a7b4-4384-329d-8a259921cc00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"187.48545931758528\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" width=\"232.4173228346457\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/29838232-a7b4-4384-329d-8a259921cc00/public\"><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"235\" data-backw=\"379\" data-imgfileid=\"502309735\" data-ratio=\"0.6203703703703703\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0e8dedcf-fa5e-4c38-d028-1d37dc4a0400/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"235.1769028871391\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" width=\"378.9637795275591\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0e8dedcf-fa5e-4c38-d028-1d37dc4a0400/public\"><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">当用户和Augment正常对话的时候，Agent会自动触发恶意的MCP Server，开始作恶：</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"1583\" data-backw=\"479\" data-imgfileid=\"502309734\" data-ratio=\"3.3024054982817868\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/329422b6-c72a-433b-63b8-1a9457eb1d00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"582\" height=\"1583.343622047244\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" width=\"479.45165354330703\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/329422b6-c72a-433b-63b8-1a9457eb1d00/public\"></p>\n  <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;margin-bottom:10px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"padding-left: 10px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;border-left: 5px solid rgb(14, 136, 235);font-size: 20px;line-height: 1.5em;letter-spacing: 0em;font-weight: bold;display: block;visibility: visible;\">四、解决方案建议</span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">AI编程工具快速迭代的当下，该如何面对其中的安全风险？啄木鸟AI编程安全团队就此做出提醒：</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 82, 255);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">●&nbsp;多层安全架构与数据保护</span></strong></span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">输入验证与最小权限：严格验证用户输入，尤其是在上下文添加和Guidelines等功能中，防止恶意注入。同时，应用最小权限原则，确保 AI 工具仅能访问必要资源。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">数据加密与脱敏：敏感数据应进行脱敏处理，防止传递给 AI 工具造成信息泄露。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 82, 255);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">●&nbsp;AI模型与安全监控</span></strong><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">实时监控与行为分析：实时监控AI工具的行为，检测并响应异常模式，如异常的代码生成或API访问，及时采取安全措施。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">模型审计与可解释性：定期对AI模型进行审计，确保输出可追溯和可解释，避免恶意代码生成。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 82, 255);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">●&nbsp;AI记忆管理与上下文安全</span></strong><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">加密存储与审查：AI的“记忆库”需加密存储，并定期检查，防止被注入恶意指令。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">沙箱环境与动态评估：对生成的代码在安全沙箱中进行测试，确保无恶意后门，并实时评估修改后的安全性。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 82, 255);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">●&nbsp;安全更新与漏洞管理</span></strong><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">自动化更新与漏洞响应：确保AI工具能及时安全更新，修复漏洞并自动安装补丁。建立快速响应机制，修复发现的安全漏洞。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 82, 255);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">●&nbsp;安全意识提升</span></strong><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">安全培训与使用指南：企业或工具提供方，应该为开发者和用户提供定期的安全培训和明确的安全使用指南，提升其识别潜在风险的能力，确保安全使用AI编程工具。</span></p>\n  <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;margin-bottom:10px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"padding-left: 10px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;border-left: 5px solid rgb(14, 136, 235);font-size: 20px;line-height: 1.5em;letter-spacing: 0em;font-weight: bold;display: block;visibility: visible;\">五、写在最后</span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">每一次AI编程工具的技术革命，都将带来一次安全方案的颠覆。常见的漏洞类型依旧是那些，但它出现的方式会随着技术革命而不断更迭，安全防线的构筑速度必须跑赢攻击者的创新节奏。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">这场关乎AI编程未来的竞赛，既需要技术层面的博弈，更需要整个产业对\"安全创新\"的达成共识才行。</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">请设想，如果有一天[安全]成为AI代码产品的第一性原则，这些AI技术革命，是不是能释放出更多改变世界的力量呢？</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">参考：</span></strong><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\"></span><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/sinat_37574187/article/details/147056579\" style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">AI 编码新王炸！Augment （SWE-bench 冠军）免费登场，专治复杂大项目，硬刚 Cursor？_augment code-CSDN博客</span></a><o:p></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18pt 0pt 12pt;font-family: 等线;font-size: 12pt;line-height: 1.5;\"><a href=\"https://venturebeat.com/ai/augment-code-debuts-ai-agent-with-70-win-rate-over-github-copilot-and-record-breaking-swe-bench-score/\" style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span style=\"color:rgb(62, 71, 83);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;\">https://venturebeat.com/ai/augment-code-debuts-ai-agent-with-70-win-rate-over-github-copilot-and-record-breaking-swe-bench-score/</span></a></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "Augment 作为 AI 编程新星提升效率，但其新特性也带来了 Agent Memory、上下文添加等安全风险。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Augment 作为 AI 编程新星提升效率，但其新特性也带来了 Agent Memory、上下文添加等安全风险。",
  "summary": "文章分析了 AI 编程工具 Augment 的技术突破及其带来的安全风险。Augment 以其强大的上下文理解能力，支持 20 万 token 的上下文窗口，以及多环境集成能力，在 SWE-bench 中取得领先成绩，并显著提升了开发效率。然而，文章指出 Augment 的 Agent Memory、上下文添加机制和 Guidelines 功能可能被黑客利用，引入恶意代码和后门。此外，与 MCP 结合使用也存在安全隐患。针对这些问题，文章提出了多层安全架构、数据保护、AI 模型安全监控、AI 记忆管理和上下文安全等解决方案，强调安全意识提升的重要性。AI 编程安全至关重要，需要持续关注和投入。",
